item.title: Fanboy
item.dc:creator: @The_Un-Named The Un-Named
item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

I only scored so high on Sony because I want MGS4. I like Nintendo, but my honest opinion on the Wii is that it is SHIT. It has NO good games, the Wiimote hurts your wrist while playing games like RE4, the extensions(nunchuck, zapper etc) are far too expensive, and the browser costing money unless you downloaded it before a certain date takes the piss. I haven’t looked at pirating games on it yet, but buying some of the older games may be fun but definitely not worth it.

I would get a PS3, but it has no backwards compatibility and I don’t fancy buying a decent tv. I could use the one I got now but it seems to have stopped working with my PS2 so yeah.

Results:

Nintendo Fanboy: 49%
Sony Fanboy: 47%
Microsoft Fanboy: 8%

The Better Fanboy Check Test
says that I’m A Microsoft Hater

What does it mean?

You aren’t a fanboy, since you love both Nintendo and Sony. But you really hate Bill Gates and everything he creates. Or at least you don’t care about anything he creates.
